      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "White Knight vs. Hunter",
        "Client": "Wandering Swordsman",
        "Description": "I am a warrior, roaming these lands\r\nto hone my skills. I\u0027ve come to the\r\nIslands to observe the so-called\r\n\u0022White Knight.\u0022 I long to challenge\r\nit, however, it is custom in my\r\ncountry to allow you the honor first.\r\nHave at it, brave Hunter!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Barioth",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Chevalier contre chasseur",
        "Client": "\u00C9p\u00E9iste itin\u00E9rant",
        "Description": "Comme tout bon guerrier qui se\r\nrespecte, je souhaite faire mes\r\narmes. Je suis \u00E0 la recherche du\r\nl\u00E9gendaire \u0022Chevalier blanc\u0022, d\u0027o\u00F9 ma\r\nvenue dans l\u0027Archipel. Je r\u00EAve de\r\nl\u0027affronter, mais la coutume veut que\r\nje te laisse tenter ta chance avant.",
        "Target": "Chasser un Barioth",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Cavaliere contro cacciatore",
        "Client": "Spadaccino errante",
        "Description": "Sono un guerriero e vago in\r\nqueste terre per migliorare le\r\nmie abilit\u00E0. Sono giunto sulle\r\nisole per osservare il\r\ncosiddetto \u0022Cavaliere bianco\u0022.\r\nGradirei combattere contro di\r\nlui, ma lascio a voi l\u0027onore.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Barioth",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Wei\u00DFer Ritter gegen Jagd-Ass",
        "Client": "Wandernder Schwertk\u00E4mpfer",
        "Description": "Als Krieger zieh ich durch die Lande,\r\num meine Kampfkunst zu verfeinern.\r\nMein Wunsch, den \u0022Wei\u00DFen Ritter\u0022\r\nzu sehen, f\u00FChrt mich her. Ich will ihn\r\nherausfordern, allerdings ist es in\r\nmeiner Heimat Brauch, dir den Vor-\r\ntritt zu lassen. Das Feld geh\u00F6rt dir.",
